Package itunesq

Class FindDuplicatesDialog

java.lang.Object
itunesq.FindDuplicatesDialog
public class FindDuplicatesDialog extends Object
Class that handles the find duplicates dialog. This dialog allows the user to find exact song duplicates, or fuzzy duplicates based on track attribute search criteria. For example:
  • Songs with the same name but different artists
  • Songs with the same name and artist but different kind (MP3 vs AAC)
  • Songs with the same name and artist but different duration
